1. Oatmeal with fruit and nuts - 2 cups of oats, 1/2 banana, 1 tbsp chia seeds, 1/4 cup of almonds or waln	
2. Turkey wrap with mixed greens and tomato - 3/4-1 whole wheat wrap, 3/4 cup of spinach, 1/2 an avocado, 1/4 red onion, 1 tbsp of hummus, 1/4-1/2 a turkey or chicken breast
3. Roasted vegetables with quinoa - 1 1/2 cup of brown rice, 1/2 cup of broccoli, 1/2 cup of asparagus, 1/2 carrots, 1/4 zucchini, 1/4 red pepper, 1/4 brussel sprouts, 2 tbsp olive oil, salt and pepper to taste
4. Grilled chicken with salad - 3/4-1 chicken breast, baked or grilled, 1/2 cup of mixed greens, 1/2 red onion, 1/2 cup cherry tomatoes, 1/2 grape tomatoes, 1/4 cucumber, 1 tbsp balsamic vinegar, 1 tsp olive oil, salt and pepper to taste
5. Greek yogurt with fruit - 8-10 ounces of plain greek yogurt, 1/2 cup of blueberries or strawberries, 1/4 banana or apple
